{{flavour|Animates some rock walls adjacent to the target — including the target itself, if it is a rock wall — to create some earth elementals.}}

'''Awaken Earth''' is a monster-only spell that turns some nearby rock walls into [[earth elemental]]s. The elementals count as [[summon]]s and are worth no experience, but the walls are permanently removed. This can quickly turn a defensive chokepoint into a death trap, as even once you've dealt with the elementals or their creator, other dangerous creatures have new ways to reach you. 

Like [[Dig]], Awaken Earth can be used outside the player's [[LOS]]. However, monsters generally won't cast it unless they know your location (if it saw you before, if you get [[mark]]ed, or if you make a [[noise]]).

The following monsters cast this spell:
*{{monsterlink|Deep elf elementalist}}

==History==
*In [[0.31]], Awaken Earth was removed.
*In [[0.18]], Awaken Earth was introduced.

